---
title: Bacon-Wrapped Salmon with Pesto Potatoes
description: We already love salmon but let's take it to the next level with a wrap and twirl in smoky bacon! Zesty pesto potatoes and slow-roasted broccolini will make tonight's meal feel like date night!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bacon-wrapped-salmon-348df49b.jpg
